    <h1>SSL certificates</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>An SSL certificate is used to encrypt your website. It provides a secure connection to your website and your online store. An SSL certificate is required for certain markets and for receiving the Trusted Shops certification. You know you’re using an SSL certificate if your website is accessed via <em>https</em>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
