<div class="title">When is the order complete?</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The order process is only finished when the status in the backend says "Complete". Any messages that include the word "challenge…​" mean that the order is still being processed. <a href="/en/business-decisions/system-administration/ssl-certificate#1400">Refer to the FAQ</a> if the order status is stuck in "challengeSolved".</p>
